     2→///
     3→/// Renders columns left-to-right: pending, running, done, failed, merged.
     4→/// Empty columns collapse to a 3-char narrow divider showing only the state
     5→/// glyph (`·`, `⚙`, `✓`, `✗`, `~`). Non-collapsed columns share remaining
     6→/// width equally via `Constraint::Fill(1)` and display a bordered `List` of
     7→/// card rows.
     8→///
     9→/// Focus and WIP indicators:
    10→/// - Focused column: `Color::Yellow` border
    11→/// - Running column ≥75% WIP: amber title
    12→/// - Running column at 100% WIP: red title + border
    13→use ratatui::layout::{Constraint, Layout, Rect};
    14→use ratatui::style::{Color, Modifier, Style};
    15→use ratatui::text::{Line, Span};
    16→use ratatui::widgets::{Block, List, ListItem, Paragraph};
