     1→/// Key input handling dispatched by current [`Mode`].
     2→///
     3→/// Each mode has its own handler function that processes [`KeyEvent`]s and
     4→/// mutates [`App`] state accordingly. The main entry point [`handle_key`]
     5→/// dispatches to the correct handler based on `app.mode`.
     6→///
     7→/// Normal mode keybindings:
     8→/// - `h` / `l` — move column focus left / right (wrapping)
     9→/// - `j` / `k` — move selected card down / up within current column
